Quaderno,allows,business,owners,to,manage,their,invoices,expenses,and,cost,estimates,from,one,online,location,Users,can,create,highly,personalized,invoices,that,can,be,designed,to,be,sent,out,once,or,on,a,recurring,basis,Quaderno,also,provides,functions,for,analyzing,income,statements,calculating,taxes,and,creating,customized,reports,Users,retain,complete,control,over,their,information,and,can,export,it,at,any,time,Information,stored,with,Quaderno,can,be,accessed,by,its,owners,via,REST,API